Interface DataSetFeature

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    StatisticsDataSet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeneralGeoDataSet, GeoDataSet

    public interface DataSetFeature
    A certain feature of a dataset, supporting a specific function set - e.g., visualization of a certain type. Type of a feature is identified by direct sub-interface of this interface.
    Author:
    Yuanchao Ma
